.TH LOOTSHEET-DB-MIGRATE 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-db-migrate \\- Apply pending embedded schema migrations
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet db migrate [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Usage:
  lootsheet db migrate

Applies pending schema migrations to the configured LootSheet database.
Foreign and damaged databases are reported and left untouched.

Examples:
  lootsheet db migrate
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
-h, --help
help for migrate
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet-db(1)
